pg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請問R730(狗隻#137604)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2111627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2111627</a><br />\n此狗隻奶共證據:<br />\n出言侮辱同路人，近日又留言指「聽到仲有人講831，真係好尷尬」。<br />\n建議而家即刻係各大屈臣氏大叫政府無能 馬上封關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eOKtbT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eOKtbT</a><br />\n太子站幕門突然碎裂  玻璃跌入路軌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atgGEHV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atgGEHV</a><br />\n<br />\n懷疑此帳號原擁有者可能已經被殺,以前反CCTVB,而家做CCTVB打手<br />\n睇CCTVB死全家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/794788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/794788</a><br />\n<br />\n老鳳宣佈沙皮狗係終極奶共狗，必須將佢成個集團所有分身清除，否則連登必死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2123735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2123735</a><br />\n此狗隻為沙皮狗分身明顯證據:<br />\n舉報會員老鳳(#48234)開分身及不停洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qatBJRX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qatBJRX</a><br />\n喺佢自己惡意舉報post表示老鳳俾佢迫到傻咗,但係忘記切換帳號<br />\n而且俾佢特別置頂,明確承認開分身<br />\n<br />\n請問沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863914</a><br />\n無恥沙皮狗(狗隻#133680)肯向香港手足道歉未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252543</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcpCtDj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcpCtDj.png&h=d95fea7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yaEZGYj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyaEZGYj.png&h=6e12e1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j8uMrdt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8uMrdt.png&h=9e16340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成撚日話老鳳洗板,梗係啦,你啲罪證咁撚多,你出現已經等於迫老鳳洗板<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙皮狗一吠，所有連登手足便都指著牠笑，有的叫道，「沙皮狗，站務台又見到你罪證了！」他不回答，自言自語，「老鳳洗板，舉報佢開分身。」便開post亂鳩咁屈。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又開了奶共的post了！」沙皮狗睜大眼睛吠，「你怎麼這樣憑空污狗清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你開了奶共post，被追擊。」沙皮狗便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯吠，「文匯大公不能算奶共&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公！&hellip;&hellip;文匯大公報的事，能算奶共麼？」接連便是難懂的嗚咽聲，什麼「老鳳推人去死」，什麼「老鳳俾我迫到傻咗」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。</span></span>"},{"pid":"7cf0e018923e0c92abb28e2599c7e455503eb84a","tid":2317150,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34b18a1549b7f63519ac0ea85e76d1f9579fa1f","tid":2317150,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"黎生會戰勝歸來"},{"pid":"0eaca99fb93767c0a32b1d4c542a77277bca25c3","tid":2317150,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:52:28.000Z","msg":"佢地成日發生咗疫症之後所講嘅「專業清潔」、「深層清潔」到底係點清潔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7747ce0724d14d08b342b74e272e5f3dea651b3d","tid":2317150,"uid":213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T01:53:56.000Z","msg":"仲唔拿拿臨封撚左黨鐵去？<br />\n又唔係第一次封"}],"pinned":{"pid":"a73fc5c595ed160550660a27b537249f84e6b214","tid":2317150,"uid":76470,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/930Zupc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F930Zupc.gif&h=b3c09670&s={SIZE}\" />"}}